{"bangumi":{"date":"2001-02-21","platform":"OVA","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/a0/9e/4028_bybZS.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/a0/9e/4028_bybZS.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/a0/9e/4028_bybZS.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/a0/9e/4028_bybZS.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/a0/9e/4028_bybZS.jpg"},"summary":"猫姐姐病重卧床，灵魂正被死神带走。猫猫弟弟拼命与死神争回姐姐的灵魂，千辛万苦却只争回一半，姐姐虽然死而复生，可是睁开眼睛的姐姐却变得痴痴傻傻。猫猫姐弟原本受妈妈所托到街市买豆腐，但他们却辗转踏上为姐姐寻找另一半灵魂的旅程。\r\n诡异的旅途中，不乏血腥与暴力，但也少不了温馨和生趣。他们遇上马戏团神奇的魔术师，穿过大海，走过沙漠，遇上大屋的奇怪主人，还遇上把猫猫残肢缝合的妇人，还有孩子脾气的上帝，随意拨弄着时间。最后他们终于找到了拯救姐姐的四叶花。","name":"ねこぢる草","name_cn":"猫汤","tags":[{"name":"汤浅政明","count":813,"total_cont":0},{"name":"OVA","count":642,"total_cont":0},{"name":"J.C.STAFF","count":570,"total_cont":0},{"name":"意识流","count":511,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2001","count":406,"total_cont":0},{"name":"黑暗童话","count":300,"total_cont":0},{"name":"内涵","count":209,"total_cont":0},{"name":"漫画改","count":158,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Studio4℃","count":148,"total_cont":0},{"name":"佐藤龙雄","count":142,"total_cont":0},{"name":"幻想","count":90,"total_cont":0},{"name":"湯浅政明","count":79,"total_cont":0},{"name":"生命","count":59,"total_cont":0},{"name":"佐藤竜雄","count":52,"total_cont":0},{"name":"漫改","count":50,"total_cont":0},{"name":"短片","count":43,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本","count":37,"total_cont":0},{"name":"奇幻","count":28,"total_cont":0},{"name":"无厘头","count":25,"total_cont":0},{"name":"猎奇","count":25,"total_cont":0},{"name":"黑暗","count":20,"total_cont":0},{"name":"致郁","count":19,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2001年","count":19,"total_cont":0},{"name":"剧场版","count":16,"total_cont":0},{"name":"cult","count":9,"total_cont":0},{"name":"猫汤","count":7,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2001年2月","count":7,"total_cont":0},{"name":"ねこぢる","count":7,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2000s","count":7,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动画电影","count":6,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"猫汤"},{"key":"话数","value":"1"},{"key":"发